casebody.data:
Mark P. DONALDSON, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH AND HUMAN SERVICES, and McLaren Health Care Corporation, Defendants-Appellees. SC: 156760
COA: 337586 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 27, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's April 3, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because it does not appear that the order was entered erroneously.
